---
title: Southeast Asian-Style Beef & Tofu Noodle Soup with Baby Broccoli & Coriander
description: On a cold wintery night, a soup is always our go-to dinner option. Strings of yummy noodles will go down smoothly with golden spiced tofu and veggies in a creamy coconut broth. This bowl of goodness will have you feeling the warmth from within in no time.
